# Every asdf-managed toolchain the repo needs, in one place. Install them all
# with `make install-tools` (adds any missing asdf plugin, then `asdf install`).
#
# Lines with more than one version: the first is the repo default; the extra is
# the older LTS the examples/ projects deliberately build against (each pins the
# exact version in its own examples/**/.tool-versions, which resolves here).
#
# Node is asdf-managed here; typescript/.node-version mirrors this exact
# version so setup-node (CI) and asdf-nodejs (which reads that legacy file
# inside typescript/) resolve the same Node the root .tool-versions installs.
#
# Not asdf-managed, so not listed — each is pinned by its own native file, and
# the workflows read those rather than naming a version:
#   Rust    rust/rust-toolchain.toml        (rustup, cargo)
#   pnpm    "packageManager" in typescript/package.json  (corepack)
adr-tools 3.0.0
dotnet 10.0.302
java temurin-25.0.3+9.0.LTS temurin-21.0.5+11.0.LTS
nodejs 26.5.0
ruby 4.0.6 3.2.2
golang 1.26.5
